Just when everything was
swept into a foggy state,

00:39:02.668 --> 00:39:05.248
she arrived.

00:39:06.518 --> 00:39:11.818
The woman who was the first victim of
the Woojeong Village serial murder case.

00:39:16.348 --> 00:39:18.908
Do you remember these people?

