00:41:12.108 --> 00:41:15.718
She's really bringing down the mood.

00:41:15.718 --> 00:41:20.748
♪ For the freedom, brandishing... ♪

00:41:20.748 --> 00:41:23.388
She's charming.

00:41:23.388 --> 00:41:24.718
Don't you think?

